1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,480
Why does being lazy feel like a sin?

2
00:00:02,480 --> 00:00:05,360
Because it was literally invented as one.

3
00:00:05,360 --> 00:00:08,880
1,600 years ago, a monk alone in the Egyptian desert

4
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:11,880
gave the feeling a name and called it a demon.

5
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:15,160
The guilt you feel on the couch traces straight back to him

6
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:17,040
and it only gets stranger from there.
